bilingual.target: 所有故事都有相似的结构。

bilingual.source: Decide on a structure and point of view for your poem.
bilingual.target: 决定你的诗的结构和观点。

bilingual.source: The Great Wall of China is the largest structure ever made.
bilingual.target: 中国的长城是有史以来建造的最大结构。

bilingual.source: The structure of the molecule resembles that of water.
bilingual.target: 这种分子的结构类似于水的结构。

bilingual.source: This structure chart shows the company's organizational structure.
bilingual.target: 这个结构图展示了公司的组织架构。
这种分子具有五元结构。
铆钉牢牢固定住了结构。
这个星系具有螺旋形结构。

bilingual.source: A tree is a common data structure.
bilingual.target: 树是一种常见的数据结构。

list.abstract: 用户定义的值类型。与类相似，结构可以包含构造函数、常数、字段、方法、属性、索引器、运算符和嵌套类型。

yingyinNormal.en: Structure, constant structure. One atom...
yingyinNormal.zh: 结构，恒定结构，一个原子……

yingyinNormal.en: Then when you come to shape it, you have a more regular structure inside your loaf.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你再次塑形的时候，你面包里面的结构就更规则。

yingyinNormal.en: Only plant cells have a cell wall, which is made of rigid cellulose that gives the plant structure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是只有植物细胞有细胞壁，当中坚硬的纤维素给植物制造了他的结构。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we were studying molecular structure, and it occurred to us that we are all made with particular molecules.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在学分子结构的时候，突然意识到自己也是由特定的分子组成的。

yingyinNormal.en: To the naked eye, a petal looks smooth. But magnify it 1,000 times and you can see its real structure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 肉眼看上去，花瓣似乎很光滑，可是放大1000倍之后，花瓣真正的结构便一览无余了。

yingyinNormal.en: Concealment becomes an art for these octopi, capable of changing the color and structure of their skin to deceive their attackers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些章鱼让隐匿成为了艺术，它们能够变换皮肤颜色和结构来迷惑敌人。

yingyinNormal.en: There can be as many as 10 million ribosomes in a human cell, all studded along a ribbon-like structure called the endoplasmic reticulum.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在一个人体细胞里有一千万个核糖体，都集中在一个叫做内质网的结构上。

yingyinNormal.en: So? They'll say it's an analogue. It's still illegal. They'll say it's substantially similar. Not in chemical structure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那又怎样，他们会说那是同类物质，还是非法的，他们会说它们本质上是相似的。但化学结构上不是。

yingyinNormal.en: The structure and evolution of galaxies, the formation of our own solar system, the make-up of earth's geography and ecosystems, our economies and markets, and each of us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 银河系的结构和演化，太阳系的形成，地球地理和生态系统的形成，我们的经济和市场我们每一个人。

yingyinNormal.en: It's really the first time I've had an objective structure around the film saying that time literally is relative that we all experience time differently depending on where we are in the universe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这真的是第一次围绕电影网有一个目标结构讲述时间实际上是相对的，我们经历的时间都不一样，取决于我们在宇宙的什么地方。

yingyinNormal.en: So if you zoom in on this genome, then what you see, of course, is this double helix structure, the code of life spelled out with these four biochemical letters, or we call them bases, right, A, C, G and T.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果放大这条基因组，你看到的当然就是这个双螺旋结构。生命的密码就是由这些生化的字母组成或者说碱基，对吧：A, C, G 和 T。

yingyinNormal.en: Rileytown has order, structure and our hands folded like so! What do you got?
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱丽镇有秩序有组织，而且我们的手还能叠成这样，你呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Inside this structure, the energy of two photons is used to split a water molecule.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这个复合体中，两个光子放射出的能量就可以使一个水分子分解。

yingyinNormal.en: One great structure that didn't rise naturally from the Earth, is China's Great Wall.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一依靠人工拔地而起的伟大建筑就是中国长城。

yingyinNormal.en: The longest man-made structure on earth runs from the Pacific Ocean to the Gobi Desert.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这世界上最长的建筑，东起渤海之滨，西至大漠戈壁。

yingyinNormal.en: So it's settled. You'll stay with us. Yeah, I'll walk you to your car. You're in structure 3, level c, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 就这么定了，你住我们这儿。我带你去拿车，你车停在3区，c层，没错吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Rising over half a mile into the sky is the breathtaking centerpiece of Dubai, The Burj Kalifa, the tallest structure ever built.
yingyinNormal.zh: 高耸入云的哈利法塔是迪拜的惊人地标，超过八百米的尖塔，是目前全球最高的建筑物。

yingyinNormal.en: Those stolen NYPD files contain every member of Elias' organization, his business associates, and the structure of his operation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那些被偷走的纽约警局文件中有全部以利亚组织的成员名单，生意伙伴以及运作架构。

yingyinNormal.en: I agree. That's why I home-school all three of my children. The conference table in our boardroom actually rests on their play structure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我同意。这就是我对孩子实施在家教育的原因。其实我们董事会的会议桌，就在他们的游乐设施旁边。

yingyinNormal.en: Asking for feedback is a really important habit to get into as you leave the structure of the school calendar and exams and grades behind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 养成寻求反馈的习惯是非常重要的。特别是在离开学校系统 没了考试和分数之后。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

vt. 组织；建造；构成；构造；（structure的过去式和过去分词）

word_family.mean: n. 结构；构造；组织；体系；机构；建筑物；结构物；条理

sense_info_list.en: the arrangement of and relations between the parts or elements of something complex

examination_example.sentence: A high growth rate placed great strains on the existing <highlight>structures</highlight> of governance, of administration, and above all of socialization.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 高增长率对现有的管理、行政、尤其是社会化结构造成很大的压力。

examination_example.sentence: He freed music from hitherto prevailing conventions of harmony and <highlight>structure</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他打破了迄今为止还在盛行的乐曲要遵从和声结构的常规惯例。

examination_example.sentence: The other reason why costs are so high is the restrictive guild-like ownership <highlight>structure</highlight> of the business.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 成本如此之高的另一个原因是限制性的行业协会式所有权结构。

examination_example.sentence: The well-<highlight>structured</highlight> daily plans would be most effective.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 良好的日常安排将是最有效的。

examination_example.sentence: Composure is a state of mind made possible by the <highlight>structuring</highlight> of one's relation to one's environment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 沉着是一种心态，这种状态可能是由构建人与自然的关系才得以实现。

sense_info_list.en: a building or other object constructed from several parts

examination_example.sentence: The total amount of damage to Notre Dame Cathedral can be assessed only when its <highlight>structure</highlight> is considered safe.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在确认大教堂结构安全之前，无法完整清点出火灾造成的损失。

examination_example.sentence: "They saved the main <highlight>structure</highlight>, but it all came down to 15-30 minutes," Nunez said.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “他们保留了主要结构，但最终只剩下15-30分钟，”努内斯说。

examination_example.sentence: Police and fire services will spend the next 48 hours assessing the "security and safety" of the 850-year-old <highlight>structure</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 警察和消防部门将在接下来的48小时内评估这座有850年历史的建筑的“安保和安全”。

examination_example.sentence: Brittleness remains a problem when building steel <highlight>structures</highlight> in cold conditions, such as oil rigs in the Arctic.
